      "content": "hi, im feeling really weird today. my chest feels super heavy like something is sitting on it and im feeling nauseous and just so exhausted. i have anxiety so i feel like maybe i'm just having a bad episode? does this sound like it could be an anxiety attack or should i be worried?",
